User Stories:
1. As a Student, I want to register an account using my student ID so that I can access the
clinic's digital services.
2. As a Student, I want to login securely so that my personal medical appointment data
remains private.
3. As a Student, I want to view available time slots for specific doctors so that I can book an
appointment that doesn't clash with my classes.
4. As a Student, I want to book an appointment so that I can secure a time to see a doctor
without waiting in a physical queue.
5. As a Student, I want to cancel an existing appointment if my plans change so that the time
slot becomes available for other students.
6. As a Doctor, I want to view my daily schedule so that I can prepare for the number of
patients I need to see.
7. As a Doctor, I want to update my availability so that students do not book slots when I am
unavailable.
8. As an Admin, I want to manage user accounts to ensure only authorized personnel and
students are using the system
9. As an Admin, I want to view all clinic schedules to identify peak times and optimize staff
allocation.
10. As a User, I want to reset my password through the "Forgot Password" feature so that I can
regain access to my account if I lose my credentials.
